":"http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail","width":"26","height":"32","src":"\/\/4.bp.blogspot.com\/-GTIh2pdzDYI\/VtcrB6rX0pI\/AAAAAAAABUg\/vWdDxEU4N6c\/s220\/Thinker.jpg"}}],"generator":{"version":"7.00","uri":"http://www.blogger.com","$t":"Blogger"},"openSearch$totalResults":{"$t":"640"},"openSearch$startIndex":{"$t":"1"},"openSearch$itemsPerPage":{"$t":"8"},"entry":[{"id":{"$t":"tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-5227376702666828549"},"published":{"$t":"2019-02-25T23:52:00.000+08:00"},"updated":{"$t":"2019-03-01T13:17:59.118+08:00"},"category":[{"scheme":"http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#","term":"书评\/影评"},{"scheme":"http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#","term":"政治"}],"title":{"type":"text","$t":"分享各类电子书（政治、哲学 等，63本）"},"summary":{"type":"text","$t":"　　又到了分享电子书的时候。这次有63本——大部分是“政治、哲学”大类，少部分是“历史、文艺、社会学、军事”大类。\n　　顺便说一下：俺采纳了某个热心读者的建议，用两种背景色分别表示“新增书籍”和“补充格式”。具体参见下面的“阅读说明”。\n\n★阅读说明\n　　对于本次【上传的】电子书，为了醒目起见，用这种颜色表示【新增书籍】；用这种颜色表示【补充格式】。\n\n　　如果你在“博客阅读器”中查看本文，并且【没】看到“带色的表格行”，不是因为你色盲，是因为某些博客阅读器无法显示这种“带颜色”的 HTML 语法。碰到此种情况，请直接【翻墙】到俺博客站点查看本博文，就可以看到“【带背景色】的表格行”。\n　　不会翻墙的同学，请猛击如下网址，查看【全部电子书清单】（这些年来，GitHub 一直可以【免翻墙】访问）\n\nhttps:\/\/github.com\/programthink\/books\n\n\n★下载的注意"},"link":[{"rel":"replies","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https:\/\/program-think.blogspot.com\/feeds\/5227376702666828549\/comments\/default","title":"博文评论"},{"rel":"replies","type":"text/html","href":"https:\/\/program-think.blogspot.com\/2019\/02\/share-books.html#comment-form","title":"238 条评论"},{"rel":"edit","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https:\/\/www.blogger.com\/feeds\/5235590154125226279\/posts\/default\/5227376702666828549"},{"rel":"self","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https:\/\/www.blogger.com\/feeds\/5235590154125226279\/posts\/default\/5227376702666828549"},{"rel":"alternate","type":"text/html","href":"https:\/\/program-think.blogspot.com\/2019\/02\/share-books.html","title":"分享各类电子书（政治、哲学 等，63本）"}],"author":[{"name":{"$t":"编程随想"},"uri":{"$t":"http:\/\/www.blogger.com\/profile\/11741356469378252621"},"email":{"$t":"noreply@blogger.com"},"gd$image":{"rel":"http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail","width":"26","height":"32","src":"\/\/4.bp.blogspot.com\/-GTIh2pdzDYI\/VtcrB6rX0pI\/AAAAAAAABUg\/vWdDxEU4N6c\/s220\/Thinker.jpg"}}],"thr$total":{"$t":"238"}},{"id":{"$t":"tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-573421185532363513"},"published":{"$t":"2019-02-14T23:56:00.000+08:00"},"updated":{"$t":"2019-02-21T18:29:34.924+08:00"},"category":[{"scheme":"http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#","term":"IT"},{"scheme":"http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#","term":"IT.信息安全"}],"title":{"type":"text","$t":"如何用“磁盘加密”对抗警方的【取证软件】和【刑讯逼供】，兼谈数据删除技巧"},"summary":{"type":"text","$t":"　　春节假期结束啦，继续来谈信息安全的话题。\n　　先顺便说俩事儿：\n1. 虽然本文与上一篇博文的间隔超过两周，但俺上一次【网络活动】是2月7日（在回复读者评论）。所以，依然属于【正常静默】。不要担心俺 :)\n2. 上一篇博文发出后，经几位热心读者提醒，俺又对“社会工程学”那个章节补充了几点内容。\n\n★引子\n　　前不久正值【开博十周年】之际，俺写了一篇《为啥朝廷总抓不到俺——十年反党活动的安全经验汇总》。\n　　今天这篇是对前一篇进行补充，主要谈——如何对付警方？看到俺写这样的东西，公安系统的“网监部门”和“技侦部门”，肯定又不爽了 :)\n\u003C!--program-think--\u003E\n\n★本文讨论的范围\n　　为了避免某些读者来抬杠，先声明一下本文讨论范围。\n\n◇面向【高风险政治人士】\n　　和前一篇博文类似，这篇也是写给“高风险政治人士”（类似俺这种反党人士）的教程。\n　　如果你有可能成为【警方】"},"link":[{"rel":"replies","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https:\/\/program-think.blogspot.com\/feeds\/573421185532363513\/comments\/default","title":"博文评论"},{"rel":"replies","type":"text/html","href":"https:\/\/program-think.blogspot.com\/2019\/02\/Use-Disk-Encryption-Anti-Computer-Forensics.html#comment-form","title":"599 条评论"},{"rel":"edit","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https:\/\/www.blogger.com\/feeds\/5235590154125226279\/posts\/default\/573421185532363513"},{"rel":"self","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https:\/\/www.blogger.com\/feeds\/5235590154125226279\/posts\/default\/573421185532363513"},{"rel":"alternate","type":"text/html","href":"https:\/\/program-think.blogspot.com\/2019\/02\/Use-Disk-Encryption-Anti-Computer-Forensics.html","title":"如何用“磁盘加密”对抗警方的【取证软件】和【刑讯逼供】，兼谈数据删除技巧"}],"author":[{"name":{"$t":"编程随想"},"uri":{"$t":"http:\/\/www.blogger.com\/profile\/11741356469378252621"},"email":{"$t":"noreply@blogger.com"},"gd$image":{"rel":"http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail","width":"26","height":"32","src":"\/\/4.bp.blogspot.com\/-GTIh2pdzDYI\/VtcrB6rX0pI\/AAAAAAAABUg\/vWdDxEU4N6c\/s220\/Thinker.jpg"}}],"thr$total":{"$t":"599"}},{"id":{"$t":"tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-2897277223911398654"},"published":{"$t":"2019-01-30T21:24:00.001+08:00"},"updated":{"$t":"2019-02-15T16:57:08.610+08:00"},"category":[{"scheme":"http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#","term":"IT"},{"scheme":"http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#","term":"IT.信息安全"}],"title":{"type":"text","$t":"为啥朝廷总抓不到俺——十年反党活动的安全经验汇总"},"summary":{"type":"text","$t":"　　好几天没上线，可能有读者以为俺出事了。别担心！俺21日还在回复评论，截止发这篇博文，【未】超出14天的期限，属于【正常静默】。\n　　因为这篇博文要【全面地】分享俺十年反党活动的【技术】经验，牵涉到很多零碎的内容，整理起来多费了点精力和时间。\n\u003C!--program-think--\u003E\n\n★“朝廷想抓俺而不可得”正说明了——俺的防御措施基本靠谱\n　　熟悉俺博客的读者都晓得——本人已经抹黑党国很多年了（从第一篇政治博文到今天，已超过“9.5年”，四舍五入就算十年吧）。\n　　俺记得很多年以前，有人在博客评论区对俺说（以下是大意）：\n你小子能在网上得瑟，是因为网监部门还没注意到你；等到哪天网警开始盯上你，你就等死吧。\n　　那时候，很多事情都还没有发生，俺缺少反驳的素材。如今可以理直气壮地反驳了——朝廷的有关部门早就盯上俺了；遗憾的是：他们拿俺一点办法也没有。\n　　想看证据的话，请围观前几天的"},"link":[{"rel":"replies","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https:\/\/program-think.blogspot.com\/feeds\/2897277223911398654\/comments\/default","title":"博文评论"},{"rel":"replies","type":"text/html","href":"https:\/\/program-think.blogspot.com\/2019\/01\/Security-Guide-for-Political-Activists.html#comment-form","title":"1168 条评论"},{"rel":"edit","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https:\/\/www.blogger.com\/feeds\/5235590154125226279\/posts\/default\/2897277223911398654"},{"rel":"self","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https:\/\/www.blogger.com\/feeds\/5235590154125226279\/posts\/default\/2897277223911398654"},{"rel":"alternate","type":"text/html","href":"https:\/\/program-think.blogspot.com\/2019\/01\/Security-Guide-for-Political-Activists.html","title":"为啥朝廷总抓不到俺——十年反党活动的安全经验汇总"}],"author":[{"name":{"$t":"编程随想"},"uri":{"$t":"http:\/\/www.blogger.com\/profile\/11741356469378252621"},"email":{"$t":"noreply@blogger.com"},"gd$image":{"rel":"http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail","width":"26","height":"32","src":"\/\/4.bp.blogspot.com\/-GTIh2pdzDYI\/VtcrB6rX0pI\/AAAAAAAABUg\/vWdDxEU4N6c\/s220\/Thinker.jpg"}}],"thr$total":{"$t":"1168"}},{"id":{"$t":"tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-2053489966989372984"},"published":{"$t":"2019-01-15T18:00:00.000+08:00"},"updated":{"$t":"2019-01-16T15:16:34.978+08:00"},"category":[{"scheme":"http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#","term":"博客通告"}],"title":{"type":"text","$t":"开博十周年庆，博文分类汇总"},"summary":{"type":"text","$t":"　　每年一次的“周年庆”又到啦！\n　　由于这次是【十周年】，有些读者建议俺搞得隆重一点。所以前几天特意发了篇《开博十周年大事记》，作为纪念。\n　　根据历年来的惯例，“周年庆”当天要发一篇【博文汇总】——把历史上的博文按照分类罗列出来，方便新来的读者了解旧博文。\u003C!--program-think--\u003E\n\n\n★对【新读者】的几项说明\n　　在切入正题之前，先插播几条说明——主要是说给【新读者】听。\n\n◇俺【无法】处理每一个“读者评论”和“读者来信”\n　　在2013年或更早，俺基本上可以做到——处理【每一条】读者评论。\n　　但如今的评论数【实在太多】，已经【无法】做到逐一回复了。\n　　至于邮件，就处理得更少了——因为评论可以被大伙儿看到，所以俺优先回复评论。如果你有【重要且紧急】的邮件发给俺，建议你在发邮件之后，再到俺博客最新的一篇博文中，用【留言的方式】提醒一下。\n　　在这里给大伙儿道个歉——"},"link":[{"rel":"replies","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https:\/\/program-think.blogspot.com\/feeds\/2053489966989372984\/comments\/default","title":"博文评论"},{"rel":"replies","type":"text/html","href":"https:\/\/program-think.blogspot.com\/2019\/01\/ten-years-blogging.html#comment-form","title":"616 条评论"},{"rel":"edit","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https:\/\/www.blogger.com\/feeds\/5235590154125226279\/posts\/default\/2053489966989372984"},{"rel":"self","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https:\/\/www.blogger.com\/feeds\/5235590154125226279\/posts\/default\/2053489966989372984"},{"rel":"alternate","type":"text/html","href":"https:\/\/program-think.blogspot.com\/2019\/01\/ten-years-blogging.html","title":"开博十周年庆，博文分类汇总"}],"author":[{"name":{"$t":"编程随想"},"uri":{"$t":"http:\/\/www.blogger.com\/profile\/11741356469378252621"},"email":{"$t":"noreply@blogger.com"},"gd$image":{"rel":"http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail","width":"26","height":"32","src":"\/\/4.bp.blogspot.com\/-GTIh2pdzDYI\/VtcrB6rX0pI\/AAAAAAAABUg\/vWdDxEU4N6c\/s220\/Thinker.jpg"}}],"thr$total":{"$t":"616"}},{"id":{"$t":"tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-3255425978908758402"},"published":{"$t":"2019-01-09T23:55:00.002+08:00"},"updated":{"$t":"2019-01-11T13:34:26.098+08:00"},"category":[{"scheme":"http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#","term":"博客通告"}],"title":{"type":"text","$t":"开博十周年大事记"},"summary":{"type":"text","$t":"　　最近的两篇博文都超长（尤其那篇《反脆弱》的读书笔记有3~4万字数，是本博有屎以来最长滴），写这两篇把俺累坏了。今天来一篇轻松点的。\n　　话说还有不到一星期，就是本博客的【十周年庆】。有些读者建议俺要有所表示，所以今天汇总一下这十年来值得纪念的事情，让列位看官（尤其是新读者）了解一下：俺能坚持到现在，也不容易啊！！！\u003C!--program-think--\u003E\n\n\n★2009年1月15日，第一篇博文——《博客开张及本博客内容简介》\n　　那天俺发了本博客【第一篇】博文（链接在“这里”），所以每年的1月15日是“开博纪念日”。\n\n　　在第一篇博文中，已经简单说了为啥会在2009年初开博客。几年之后（2013），针对某读者的提问，又专门写了篇博文，从心理学层面谈自己的动机：\n《为啥俺要写这个博客——动机的自我分析》\n\n\n★2009年2月初，开始启用【CSDN】上的博客镜像\n　　说起 CSDN，这"},"link":[{"rel":"replies","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https:\/\/program-think.blogspot.com\/feeds\/3255425978908758402\/comments\/default","title":"博文评论"},{"rel":"replies","type":"text/html","href":"https:\/\/program-think.blogspot.com\/2019\/01\/Memorabilia.html#comment-form","title":"520 条评论"},{"rel":"edit","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https:\/\/www.blogger.com\/feeds\/5235590154125226279\/posts\/default\/3255425978908758402"},{"rel":"self","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https:\/\/www.blogger.com\/feeds\/5235590154125226279\/posts\/default\/3255425978908758402"},{"rel":"alternate","type":"text/html","href":"https:\/\/program-think.blogspot.com\/2019\/01\/Memorabilia.html","title":"开博十周年大事记"}],"author":[{"name":{"$t":"编程随想"},"uri":{"$t":"http:\/\/www.blogger.com\/profile\/11741356469378252621"},"email":{"$t":"noreply@blogger.com"},"gd$image":{"rel":"http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail","width":"26","height":"32","src":"\/\/4.bp.blogspot.com\/-GTIh2pdzDYI\/VtcrB6rX0pI\/AAAAAAAABUg\/vWdDxEU4N6c\/s220\/Thinker.jpg"}}],"thr$total":{"$t":"520"}},{"id":{"$t":"tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-6213582503989759355"},"published":{"$t":"2018-12-29T23:58:00.001+08:00"},"updated":{"$t":"2019-01-15T18:15:40.708+08:00"},"category":[{"scheme":"http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#","term":"外交"},{"scheme":"http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#","term":"政治"},{"scheme":"http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#","term":"时事评论"},{"scheme":"http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#","term":"经济"},{"scheme":"http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#","term":"转载"}],"title":{"type":"text","$t":"每周转载：盘点一下贸易战爆发后的【中美对抗】（2018年4季度）"},"summary":{"type":"text","$t":"\n（这是《经济学人》某期的封面插图，图中的龙头嵌入了美国国徽中的白头鹰，暗喻【中美对抗】）\n★引子\n　　今天这篇《每周转载》，可以看作《从量变到质变——中美关系40年》一文的后续补充。\n　　在半年前（2018年7月）的那篇博文中，俺反复强调——【2018年是历史性的分水岭】。可惜很多读者对此没有引起重视。所以俺才发出今天这篇博文，汇总一下最近几个月，与【中美对抗】相关的新闻。看完之后，希望你能意识到——“历史性分水岭”一词的含义。\n\u003C!--program-think--\u003E\n\n★10月份的新闻\n◇10月2日，美国防部透露：中美两国军舰在南中国海对峙\n美国国防官员透露——\n美国海军“迪凯特”号导弹驱逐舰9月30日在争议性的南沙群岛附近实施“航行与飞越自由”任务，一艘中国旅洋级驱逐舰逼近到迪凯特号45码（约41米）之内。美舰最终为了避免碰撞而改变航向。\n美国太平洋舰队发言人查尔斯·布朗称：我们"},"link":[{"rel":"replies","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https:\/\/program-think.blogspot.com\/feeds\/6213582503989759355\/comments\/default","title":"博文评论"},{"rel":"replies","type":"text/html","href":"https:\/\/program-think.blogspot.com\/2018\/12\/weekly-share-127.html#comment-form","title":"975 条评论"},{"rel":"edit","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https:\/\/www.blogger.com\/feeds\/5235590154125226279\/posts\/default\/6213582503989759355"},{"rel":"self","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https:\/\/www.blogger.com\/feeds\/5235590154125226279\/posts\/default\/6213582503989759355"},{"rel":"alternate","type":"text/html","href":"https:\/\/program-think.blogspot.com\/2018\/12\/weekly-share-127.html","title":"每周转载：盘点一下贸易战爆发后的【中美对抗】（2018年4季度）"}],"author":[{"name":{"$t":"编程随想"},"uri":{"$t":"http:\/\/www.blogger.com\/profile\/11741356469378252621"},"email":{"$t":"noreply@blogger.com"},"gd$image":{"rel":"http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail","width":"26","height":"32","src":"\/\/4.bp.blogspot.com\/-GTIh2pdzDYI\/VtcrB6rX0pI\/AAAAAAAABUg\/vWdDxEU4N6c\/s220\/Thinker.jpg"}}],"thr$total":{"$t":"975"}},{"id":{"$t":"tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-352322624739404590"},"published":{"$t":"2018-12-17T23:56:00.001+08:00"},"updated":{"$t":"2018-12-26T23:50:10.061+08:00"},"category":[{"scheme":"http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#","term":"书评\/影评"},{"scheme":"http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#","term":"心理学"},{"scheme":"http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#","term":"政治"},{"scheme":"http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#","term":"教育"},{"scheme":"http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#","term":"经济"},{"scheme":"http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#","term":"职场点滴"}],"title":{"type":"text","$t":"读书笔记：《反脆弱——从不确定性中获益》"},"summary":{"type":"text","$t":"★引子\n　　开博这些年，俺在博客上写了一些书评，推荐了一些自认为比较好的书籍。之前的书评，采用的【形式】是：用一篇博文对某本书进行“简介”，由于只是简单介绍，每篇博文的篇幅都不长。\n　　最近几个月，俺在尝试一些【新的形式】。比如前不久（2018年9月）写的那篇《为什么马克思是错的？——全面批判马列主义的知名著作导读》，其【形式】是——用一篇比较长的博文来对某个领域的主要著作进行点评。这样一来，你就可以通过这篇博文，对该领域的【知识结构】及【知名著作】有一个大致的了解。然后你就可以判断——哪些书值得你看，哪些不值得你看。在你认为值得一看的书中，也可以决定自己的阅读顺序。\n　　今天这篇是俺的另一个尝试——采用【读书笔记】的形式向列位看官介绍某本书。这篇读书笔记，首先是写给俺自己看的，然后才是给读者看的。一般来说，只有当俺觉得某本书比较有价值并且值得阅读【多次】，才会考虑写“读书笔记”。当俺在"},"link":[{"rel":"replies","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https:\/\/program-think.blogspot.com\/feeds\/352322624739404590\/comments\/default","title":"博文评论"},{"rel":"replies","type":"text/html","href":"https:\/\/program-think.blogspot.com\/2018\/12\/Book-Review-Antifragile-Things-That-Gain-from-Disorder.html#comment-form","title":"768 条评论"},{"rel":"edit","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https:\/\/www.blogger.com\/feeds\/5235590154125226279\/posts\/default\/352322624739404590"},{"rel":"self","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https:\/\/www.blogger.com\/feeds\/5235590154125226279\/posts\/default\/352322624739404590"},{"rel":"alternate","type":"text/html","href":"https:\/\/program-think.blogspot.com\/2018\/12\/Book-Review-Antifragile-Things-That-Gain-from-Disorder.html","title":"读书笔记：《反脆弱——从不确定性中获益》"}],"author":[{"name":{"$t":"编程随想"},"uri":{"$t":"http:\/\/www.blogger.com\/profile\/11741356469378252621"},"email":{"$t":"noreply@blogger.com"},"gd$image":{"rel":"http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail","width":"26","height":"32","src":"\/\/4.bp.blogspot.com\/-GTIh2pdzDYI\/VtcrB6rX0pI\/AAAAAAAABUg\/vWdDxEU4N6c\/s220\/Thinker.jpg"}}],"thr$total":{"$t":"768"}},{"id":{"$t":"tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-5771306945628171262"},"published":{"$t":"2018-12-06T23:57:00.000+08:00"},"updated":{"$t":"2018-12-07T00:47:53.265+08:00"},"category":[{"scheme":"http://www.blogger.com/atom/ns#","term":"博客通告"}],"title":{"type":"text","$t":"告别 Google Plus——早年在 G+ 上的“每周转载”已搬运到博客主站"},"summary":{"type":"text","$t":"★G+ 的死刑\n　　2个月前（10月8日），Google Plus 曝光了一个安全漏洞，会导致用户数据泄露。借着这事儿，Google 官方顺势宣布了 G+ 的死刑。说详细点就是——G+ 的“消费者版本”将会在2019年8月关闭（参见 Google 官方博客的“这个链接”）。\u003C!--program-think--\u003E\n　　稍微了解 G+ 的用户，都知道它好景不长了。最近这几年，G+ 的人气低迷，被戏称为【鬼城】。这次曝光的安全漏洞，只不过是压跨骆驼的最后一根稻草。\n\n\n★俺的 G+ 帐号曾经用来干啥？\n　　“编程随想”这个身份很早就开始尝试 G+ 的 SNS 功能。但因为 G+ 有一个很蛋疼的“用户名规则”，要求 G+ 的用户名必须【看上去像】真实的（也就是说，不能使用明显的【化名】）。而“编程随想”这个名字一看就是【化名】。所以俺的 G+ 帐号在2012年3月惨遭 Google 管理员冻结"},"link":[{"rel":"replies","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https:\/\/program-think.blogspot.com\/feeds\/5771306945628171262\/comments\/default","title":"博文评论"},{"rel":"replies","type":"text/html","href":"https:\/\/program-think.blogspot.com\/2018\/12\/Google-Plus-Is-Dead.html#comment-form","title":"414 条评论"},{"rel":"edit","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https:\/\/www.blogger.com\/feeds\/5235590154125226279\/posts\/default\/5771306945628171262"},{"rel":"self","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https:\/\/www.blogger.com\/feeds\/5235590154125226279\/posts\/default\/5771306945628171262"},{"rel":"alternate","type":"text/html","href":"https:\/\/program-think.blogspot.com\/2018\/12\/Google-Plus-Is-Dead.html","title":"告别 Google Plus——早年在 G+ 上的“每周转载”已搬运到博客主站"}],"author":[{"name":{"$t":"编程随想"},"uri":{"$t":"http:\/\/www.blogger.com\/profile\/11741356469378252621"},"email":{"$t":"noreply@blogger.com"},"gd$image":{"rel":"http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail","width":"26","height":"32","src":"\/\/4.bp.blogspot.com\/-GTIh2pdzDYI\/VtcrB6rX0pI\/AAAAAAAABUg\/vWdDxEU4N6c\/s220\/Thinker.jpg"}}],"thr$total":{"$t":"414"}}]}}